  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Like with \"<i>real\"</i> bowling, the goal is simple: <u>Hit the Pins!</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOWLOUT is a singleplayer First-Person-Shooter set in a Pin-infested Bowling centre. Use your many, many Bowling Balls to take them out and destroy their leader in this short but satisfying adventure!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>FIRE AWAY!</u></strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw some Bowling Balls... no, I mean LOTS of Bowling Balls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/fbe3d459c4c6c2066185b64cf1fbf291.poster.avif?t=1736371805\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/fbe3d459c4c6c2066185b64cf1fbf291.webm?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/fbe3d459c4c6c2066185b64cf1fbf291.mp4?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>TOTEMS BEGONE!</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These unique enemies summon more pins. Break them ASAP! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/bcb998c802f4a74265a6c14c62aab7a6.poster.avif?t=1736371805\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/bcb998c802f4a74265a6c14c62aab7a6.webm?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/bcb998c802f4a74265a6c14c62aab7a6.mp4?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>FEATURES:</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>To ball or not to ball:</strong></i><strong> </strong>Chucking balls affects accuracy - adjust your playstyle carefully.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Who you callin' pinhead:</strong></i> Grab pins for powerful melee attacks or a piercing throw. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Shower me in medals:</strong></i><strong> </strong>Unlock various achievements by playing well... or not so well.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>My eyes are up here:</strong></i><strong> </strong>Obtain and equip different ball colors by unlocking achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>A master on the sticks:</strong></i> Use a controller to feel it rumble as you shatter groups of pins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All eyes on Deck: </strong>While not (yet) verified, BOWLOUT plays great on Steam Deck.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WARNING: Many bowling pins were harmed during the creation of this game!</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Like with \"<i>real\"</i> bowling, the goal is simple: <u>Hit the Pins!</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOWLOUT is a singleplayer First-Person-Shooter set in a Pin-infested Bowling centre. Use your many, many Bowling Balls to take them out and destroy their leader in this short but satisfying adventure!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>FIRE AWAY!</u></strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw some Bowling Balls... no, I mean LOTS of Bowling Balls!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/fbe3d459c4c6c2066185b64cf1fbf291.poster.avif?t=1736371805\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/fbe3d459c4c6c2066185b64cf1fbf291.webm?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/fbe3d459c4c6c2066185b64cf1fbf291.mp4?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>TOTEMS BEGONE!</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These unique enemies summon more pins. Break them ASAP! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/bcb998c802f4a74265a6c14c62aab7a6.poster.avif?t=1736371805\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/bcb998c802f4a74265a6c14c62aab7a6.webm?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191160/extras/bcb998c802f4a74265a6c14c62aab7a6.mp4?t=1736371805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>FEATURES:</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>To ball or not to ball:</strong></i><strong> </strong>Chucking balls affects accuracy - adjust your playstyle carefully.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Who you callin' pinhead:</strong></i> Grab pins for powerful melee attacks or a piercing throw. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Shower me in medals:</strong></i><strong> </strong>Unlock various achievements by playing well... or not so well.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>My eyes are up here:</strong></i><strong> </strong>Obtain and equip different ball colors by unlocking achievements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>A master on the sticks:</strong></i> Use a controller to feel it rumble as you shatter groups of pins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All eyes on Deck: </strong>While not (yet) verified, BOWLOUT plays great on Steam Deck.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WARNING: Many bowling pins were harmed during the creation of this game!</strong></h2>",
