      "playtime_at_review": 11,
      "review_text": "What a fantastic game, especially for the Steam Deck. It runs smooth and plays well. It's a good looking game and is fun to play, even though it's quite a simple game. \n\nSome ideas for future updates:\nI'd like to see more Todo. A simple multiplayer mode where several players can blast pins. \nWave-based survival with progression, such as bowling ball upgrades that increase strength. \nMore maps, maybe bowling alleys in different settings. \n\nHighly recommend this game",
      "timestamp_created": 1753647639
    },
